headlines.description: — Paolo Banchero had 26 points and 12 rebounds, Orlando's Wagner brothers combined for 43 points and the Magic dealt the Milwaukee Bucks their second straight loss, 112-97 on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Paolo Banchero and Wagner brothers power Magic to a 112-97 win over Bucks

headlines.description: — Jaylen Brown scored 29 points, Jayson Tatum had 27 and the Boston Celtics cruised to a 117-94 victory over the Toronto Raptors on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jaylen Brown scores 29, Jayson Tatum 27 to lead Celtics to easy 117-94 win over Toronto

headlines.description: — Bam Adebayo scored 26 points with 17 rebounds and rookie Jaime Jaquez Jr. added a career-high 20 points as the short-handed Miami Heat beat the Atlanta Hawks 117-109 on Saturday night...
headlines.shortLinkText: Adebayo scores 26 points as depleted Heat show off depth in 117-109 win over Hawks

events.name: Cleveland Cavaliers at Golden State Warriors

headlines.description: — The Cleveland Cavaliers stayed poised when things turned testy, and that showed J.B. Bickerstaff plenty about his team at this early stage.
headlines.shortLinkText: Donovan Mitchell, Cavs take down Stephen Curry and Warriors 118-110
